{"id": "art-1541", "label": "Art. 1541", "title": "Art. 1541: Comunicarea hotărârilor judecătoreşti", "slug": "art-1541", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1625640991\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1323\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1625640991\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 154<sup>1</sup>:\nComunicarea hot&#259;rârilor judec&#259;tore&#351;ti </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1060479453\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1322\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1060479453\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Comunicarea hot&#259;rârilor judec&#259;tore&#351;ti se\nva face, din oficiu, prin po&#351;t&#259; electronic&#259; dac&#259; partea a\nindicat instan&#355;ei datele corespunz&#259;toare în acest scop direct sau la\nsolicitarea expres&#259; a instan&#355;ei în timpul procesului. Comunicarea va\nfi semnat&#259; cu o semn&#259;tur&#259; electronic&#259; calificat&#259; sau o\nsemn&#259;tur&#259; electronic&#259; avansat&#259; creat&#259; cu un certificat\npentru semn&#259;tur&#259; electronic&#259; emis de o autoritate sau o\ninstitu&#355;ie public&#259; din România, care va înlocui &#351;tampila\ninstan&#355;ei &#351;i semn&#259;tura grefierului de &#351;edin&#355;&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1944967944\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1321\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1944967944\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Hot&#259;rârile judec&#259;tore&#351;ti se\nconsider&#259; comunicate la momentul la care au primit mesaj din partea\nsistemului folosit c&#259; au ajuns la destinatar potrivit datelor furnizate de\nacesta.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_475877668\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1320\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_475877668\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; comunicarea prin po&#351;t&#259;\nelectronic&#259; nu este posibil&#259; din pricina lipsei datelor în acest sens\nsau sistemul folosit indic&#259; eroare în transmiterea prin po&#351;t&#259;\nelectronic&#259;, comunicarea hot&#259;rârilor judec&#259;tore&#351;ti se va\nface potrivit art. 154.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}